Cadiz Inc.


            
            Cadiz, Inc. operates as a land and water resource development company. It engages in the acquisition, development of land with water resources for various uses such as groundwater supply, groundwater storage and agriculture. Its project include the Cadiz Valley Water Conservation, Recovery and Storage. The company was founded by Keith Brackpool in 1983 and is headquartered in Los Angeles, CA.

            
